name: TeeTick
tag_list: personalized-t-shirts, t-shirts, custom-t-shirts, tee-shirts, printed-t-shirts, personalized-clothing
overview:
TeeTick makes quality personalized clothing designed by you.

Business owners that are searching for an affordable branding option will surely find TeeTick extremely helpful. This private label clothing manufacturer, which is based in Vietnam, offers quality clothes that may be personalized with logos, text and images. TeeTick customizes t-shirts, polo shirts, hoodies, hats and just about any type of garment worn by men, women and children. TeeTick accepts both small and large orders. They bring together skills in sourcing fabric, sewing, printing, embroidery, labeling to ensure the clothing they manufacture helps their clients to stand out from the crowd.

TeeTick will be the right place for you to order a small run of your own private label clothes at low cost. TeeTick has a rapidly growing network of customers based throughout the USA, UK, Canada, Australia, New Zealand…
